data.name: SetExpression
desc: specifies service of an expression text field.

properties.name: Content
desc: contains the textual content of the field.

properties.name: CurrentPresentation
desc: contains the current content of the text field.
This property is especially useful for import/export purposes.

properties.name: Hint
desc: contains an informational text that is displayed at the user interface if it's an input field.

properties.name: IsFixedLanguage
desc: determines whether changes in language attributes at the position the text field is located also change the number format as appropriate for this language.

properties.name: IsInput
desc: determines whether this field is an input field.

properties.name: IsShowFormula
desc: determines whether the content is displayed or evaluated.

properties.name: IsVisible
desc: determines whether the field is visible.

properties.name: NumberFormat
desc: this is the number format for this field.

properties.name: NumberingType
desc: specifies the type of the numbering as com.sun.star.style.NumberingType

properties.name: SequenceValue
desc: contains the sequence value when this field is used as sequence field.

properties.name: SubType
desc: determines the type of the variable as described in com.sun.star.text.SetVariableType

properties.name: Value
desc: contains the numerical value of the field.

properties.name: VariableName
desc: contains the name of the set expression field master this field is connected to.
